      <div class="message-box"><div style="font-size:14px">From:</div><div style="font-weight:700;margin-top:6px">Someone who adores you üíå</div><div class="emoji-row"><span>üòç</span><span>ü•∞</span><span>üòò</span><span>üå∏</span><span>üç´</span></div></div>
